<div id="why_and_how">
  <div class="row_fluid">
    <h1 class='title'>Questions?</h1>
    <div id="left_why">
    <p id='qa_q_why' class='qa_questions qa_q_selected'>WHY SHOULD I DO THIS?</P>
    <p id='qa_q_webdesigncompany' class='qa_questions'>WHY NOT USE A WEB DESIGN COMPANY?</P>
    <p id='qa_q_howlong' class='qa_questions'>HOW LONG DOES IT TAKE?</P>
    <p id='qa_q_howmuch' class='qa_questions'>HOW MUCH DOES IT COST?</P>
    <p id='qa_q_whatdoiget' class='qa_questions'>WHAT DO I GET FOR MY MONEY?</P>
    <p id='qa_q_dontlike' class='qa_questions'>WHAT IF I DON'T LIKE WHAT THEY DO?</P>
    </div>
    <div id='right_why'>
      <div id='qa_why' class='qa_answers' style='display:block'>
      We've seen website owners get 'tired' of their perfectly good websites much too often, 
      deciding to do a full re-design that is both costly and time consuming. Get an objective opinion
      about whether your site really needs a full re-design, or whether a few tweaks will get the job done.
      </div>
      <div id='qa_webdesigncompany' class='qa_answers'> 
      Asking a web design company if you need a new website is like asking a hairdresser if you need a 
      haircut - the answer is always yes! 
      <br /><br />
      Input Farm's experts are not looking to sell you a site re-design (in fact they'll never try to sell
      you further paid services). Instead they'll look for the 'low hanging fruit' - how to make your site
      better with the least amount of effort. Once you receive the review you can either make the changes
      yourself or get your designer to do it for you.
      </div>
      <div id='qa_howlong' class='qa_answers'>
      No more than 72 hours.
      </div> 
      <div id='qa_howmuch' class='qa_answers'>
      <strong>$75</strong><br />
      <p>
      But good designers often charge 2-3x this amount, how does that work? <br /><br />
      InputFarm removes all the extraneous work that a designer would ordinarily have to do - quotes,
      client meetings, client communications and reports. This 'unbillable' work turns up as
      a higher hourly rate.
      <br /><br />
      By removing all this extra work they can provide this service at a very reasonable rate.
      </div>

      <div id='qa_whatdoiget' class='qa_answers'>
      Your site will be reviewed by an expert for 30 minutes and they give you a report
      containing:
      <ul style='padding-left:20px'>
        <li>Annotated markup of your site</li>
        <li>What they think is good about your site</li>
        <li>What could be improved and how</li>
        <li>The first 3 things they would do if they were working on it</li>
      </ul>
      <br />
      See a sample report now: 
        <%=link_to 'sample #1','/sample_report/1', :class=>"green_links"%> | 
        <%=link_to 'sample #2','/sample_report/2', :class=>"green_links"%>
      </div>
    
      <div id='qa_dontlike' class='qa_answers'>
        A money back guarantee is offered if you don't think you received value from Input Farm.
      </div>
    </div>
